timeline.bodyText: What do you mean by Resused? Shouldn't it be Reusable?

replies.bodyText: @Runemoro because it automatically skips back to the start of the delegate audio stream when the delegate audio stream is empty, hence reused not reusable, maybe reusing?

call it Repeating Audio Stream
